Package: shinyRadioMatrix
Type: Package
Title: R Shiny input: matrix of radio buttons
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anton Malko
Maintainer: Anton Malko <amalko@umd.edu>
Description: An input controller for R Shiny: a matrix of radio buttons,
    where exactly one option per row can be selected. It extends the radioButtons 
    controller in the base Shiny, allowing to create something akin to Likert scales.
